description: Options for exporting image data to the EPS document.

properties.description: Exports high-resolution data. Note: Use when the file will be printed on a high-resolution output device.
properties.name: ALL_IMAGE_DATA

properties.description: Exports only screen-resolution versions (72 dpi) of placed bitmap images. Note: Use in conjunction with OPI image replacement or if the resulting file will be viewed on-screen.
properties.name: PROXY_IMAGE_DATA
